<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>bellwether: glossary</title>
<style>
  :root { color-scheme: light dark; --fg: #1a1a1a; --bg: #fcfcfc; --muted: #5a5a5a; --accent: #0066cc; --border: #e0e0e0; --code-bg: rgba(127,127,127,0.10); }
  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    :root { --fg: #e8e8e8; --bg: #0f0f0f; --muted: #999; --accent: #6db3ff; --border: #2a2a2a; }
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", system-ui, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--fg); background: var(--bg); margin: 0; padding: 1rem; }
  main, header, footer { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
  header { padding: 1.5rem 0 1rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 1.7rem; }
  h1 a { color: var(--fg); text-decoration: none; }
  nav a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; margin-right: 1.25rem; font-weight: 500; }
  nav a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  main h2 { margin-top: 2rem; padding-bottom: 0.25rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); font-size: 1.2rem; }
  main h3 { margin-top: 1.5rem; font-size: 1.05rem; }
  code { font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, monospace; background: var(--code-bg); padding: 0.05rem 0.3rem; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 0.92em; }
  a { color: var(--accent); }
  footer { margin-top: 3rem; padding-top: 1rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.85rem; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <h1><a href="index.html">bellwether</a></h1>
  <nav>
    <a href="index.html">Leaderboard</a>
    <a href="methodology.html">Methodology</a>
    <a href="https://github.com/cartesianxr7/bellwether">GitHub</a>
  </nav>
</header>

<main>
{{ glossary_html_body|safe }}
</main>

<footer>
  <p>For formal definitions see the <a href="methodology.html">methodology</a>.</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
